nodes.text: The Eastern Watchwoods was the name given to the eastern part of the forest located on the northern edge of the Gormak Lands on the planet Voss, at the foot of the mountain where Voss-Ka was located. The Republic's Camp Talanis was located on the eastern edge of the Eastern Watchwoods, while the Koss Overlook marked the border between the Eastern and Western Watchwoods.
